      "content": "it just doesnt feel like something i can \"reframe\". i see the way they look at me when i mess up or when i cant provide what they need, and it just feels like i'm dragging them down. like, they deserve a parent who actually has it together, not someone who's just a constant weight on them. i feel like i'm just holding them back from being happy.",
